spec_data.Name: golang-github-influxdb-go-cache-devel
spec_data.Description:
An in-memory key:value store/cache (similar to Memcached) library for Go,
suitable for single-machine applications

This package contains library source intended for
building other packages which use influxdb/go-cache.
